entries.text: Today, Brett, Makiko and I got together to finish coding up part of assignment 6. There was a lot of work that needed to be done, and we got it done in record time! It felt super good.

Today sucked. I was totally ready to go to bed when I got a text saying I needed to show up to this random party that I wasn't going to go to. And then I had to go because I wanted to support my friends, but it turned out to be super exhausting. I mean, parties are great, but it just isn't that great when you're ready for bed...
Had an awesome coffee date with Brett and Neli today <3 Love my team
I had an awesome day today when I was able to quickly find the json library I was looking for. It's the small joys in life that really make it... I should learn to appreciate the little things more.

Got in a fight with my mom today. It sucked. I know I love her and all, but sometimes the things she say frustrate me to no end. Ugh. Wish I could be mature enough of a person to appreciate it but damn sometimes it's super annoying...
